snippet.title: NES Longplay [674] Super Spike V'Ball
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Genbu

My older brother has this game and when I was younger this was a hard game to play. I learned later into the game that I could charge my spike hits. this made the game even funner when I started smacking the players around. Hope you enjoy. -
